name: Fly or Die! (itch)
description:
This game was made for "Can you Survive this Jam? 2017"

Can you survive in this cruel world of newspapers, watermelons and cheeses? Let's find out!

Watch out for fatigue, eat pieces of cheese and watermelon. But the most important thing is to survive!

Sound of fire: Synthetic Fire Effect by Porphyr / CC BY 3.0
